definition: and/furthermore/also/together with/(not) at all/simultaneously/to combine/to join/to merge
and/moreover/yet/for the time being/to be about to/both (... and...)

sentences.english: He won a few headers and calmed things down.
sentences.chinese: 贏得了幾次頭球爭頂並且使情況穩定下來。

sentences.english: However, Toni, who knows Ribery well, believes the Bianconeri should sign him.
sentences.chinese: 然而託尼很瞭解裏貝里，並且相信尤文會簽下他。

sentences.english: And light multitaskers might be better at preserving their attention.
sentences.chinese: 並且輕度的一心多用者可能更擅長保持注意力。

sentences.english: I also worked at an insurance company for my graduate field work.
sentences.chinese: 並且我在一家保險公司進行了我的畢業設計。

sentences.english: He always optimistic and genially treats the others.
sentences.chinese: 他總是樂觀的，並且和善地對待別人。

sentences.english: I have chills and a headache.
For example: R1 service door upper guide and door latch on doorframe is worn.
sentences.chinese: R1服務門上導軌和門框的門閂陳舊並且磨損。

sentences.english: And they should carry on the self-innovation constantly and pay attention to form the fund brand.
sentences.chinese: 並且要不斷進行自我創新，注重打造基金品牌。

sentences.english: And, yes, you should create lightweight models of your proposed software designs.
sentences.chinese: 並且，你應該創建軟件設計的輕量級模型。

sentences.english: We will take good care and properly protect the patients vulnerable.
sentences.chinese: 並且對於易受傷害患者予以優先照顧和妥善保護。

sentences.english: The law was put into effect through angels by a mediator.
sentences.chinese: 並且是借天使經中保之手設立的。

sentences.english: It said people should cover their mouths when outside and keep doors and windows closed.
sentences.chinese: 還說人們外出時應該遮好嘴巴並且關好門窗。

sentences.english: Coal tar has a strong smell and can stain clothing.
sentences.chinese: 煤焦油有很強烈的氣味，並且會染污衣服。

sentences.english: Palmer knows that Drazen is holding Kimberly and wants him dead.
sentences.chinese: 帕默知道德拉贊一夥捉住了金姆，並且想要他的命。

sentences.english: It was dusk when the hunter drove into the barn and unhitched his horse.
sentences.chinese: 當獵人駕駛入穀倉並且放鬆了他的馬，它是黃昏。

sentences.english: The bladder is thin-walled and closed by a one-way valve.
sentences.chinese: 浮囊具有薄壁的結構並且通過單方向的閥門關閉。

definition: and/furthermore/also/together with/(not) at all/simultaneously/to combine/to join/to merge
to be capable of/to be able to/can
not only (this one)/not just (...) but also
to yield/to permit/to let sb do sth/to have sb do sth/to make sb (feel sad etc)/by (indicates the agent in a passive clause, like 被[bei4])
regarding/as far as sth is concerned/with regards to
only natural/as it should be/certainly/of course/without doubt
